\begin_layout Plain Layout

[幂零算子、幂零指数]
\end_layout

\end_inset

对于 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{B}\in\mathcal{L}(\mathcal{W})$
\end_inset

，若存在正整数 
\begin_inset Formula $l$
\end_inset

 使得 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{B}^{l}=\hat{0}$
\end_inset

 且 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{B}^{l-1}\neq\hat{0}$
\end_inset

，则称 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{B}$
\end_inset

 为“幂零算子 (nilpotent operator)”，并称 
\begin_inset Formula $l$
\end_inset

