\begin_inset Formula $\Span\begin{Bmatrix}\hat{B}^{l-1}\vec{w} & \hat{B}^{l-2}\vec{w} & \cdots & \hat{B}\vec{w} & \vec{w}\end{Bmatrix}$
\end_inset

